When the services are developed to be shared with other developers and investigation groups, it is a good idea to
present the data types used by the services into its own package.

Orchestrators can then add a dependency on the data type package to send requests to the services, without downloading
all the services implementation dependencies.

So, if TriDAS team decides to use it's own data type then here will go code for that particular data type serialization,
with defined mime-type. The local CmakeList.txt will creat an appropriate shared lib.